  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Jinchuuriki.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You've reached a powerful state of synchronization with your Sealed Beast, using its power but not being overwhelmed or influenced by it. You are surrounded by a light aura of Twisted Chakra that resembles a light flame of your Twisted Chakra's color and your features only change minimally. When you successfully obtain Twisted Chakra after triggering the Desperate Times feature and pass a Desperate Rage Check, you exit Desperate Rage and instead gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>If you are at 0 hit points when you enter Controlled Rage, you regain a number of Hit Points equal to 30 times your level in this Class Mod.</li><li>Increase your Strength and Dexterity Scores by +2.</li><li>Your Unarmed Damage Die becomes a d10.</li><li>Your movement speed is increased by 20 feet.</li><li>You gain a +2 bonus to Saving Throws.</li></ul><p>This feature ends as soon as you run out of Twisted Chakra, all hostile enemies flee or are defeated, 1 minute passes, or you end it as an Action, whichever happens first.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
